      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical and FDA in-house FEA solver operate under documented QA plans with version control and regression testing.",
      "rationale": "All three FEA platforms (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) are under formal software quality management systems with documented validation protocols, version tracking, and change control procedures."
    },
    {
