    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors were assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed the required credibility level. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted given the multi-laboratory validation design, the conformance of all QoIs to pre-established acceptance bounds, and the medium model risk level. Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory acceptance of the FEA framework for this COU.",
